ZH: 这条便道通往市中心。
EN: This path leads to the city center.

ZH: 便道上开满了鲜花。
EN: The path is lined with fresh flowers.

ZH: 在便道上慢慢地走。
EN: Walk slowly on the path.

ZH: 这条便道不通车。
EN: This path is not for vehicles.

ZH: 她每天都在便道上晨跑。
EN: She goes for a morning run on the path every day.

ZH: 今天的便道很拥挤。
EN: The path is crowded today.

ZH: 便道上有很多绿树。
EN: There are many green trees along the path.

ZH: 沿着便道走，你就会看到湖边。
EN: Follow the path and you will see the lake.

ZH: 便道两旁都是小商店。
EN: There are small shops on both sides of the path.

ZH: 我们在便道上散步聊天。
EN: We walk and chat on the path.

ZH: 他们在便道上骑自行车。
EN: They ride their bikes on the path.

ZH: 便道上铺着青石。
EN: The path is paved with bluestones.

ZH: 这个小村庄只有一条便道通向外界。
EN: This small village has only one path leading to the outside world.

ZH: 便道下面有一条小溪。
EN: There is a stream under the path.

ZH: 便道的尽头是一座小山。
EN: At the end of the path is a small mountain.

ZH: 他在便道上找到了一只迷失的小猫。
EN: He found a lost kitten on the path.

ZH: 我们经过便道来到了一个美丽的花园。
EN: We arrived at a beautiful garden through the path.

ZH: 在这个便道上走得太疾步会摔倒。
EN: Walking too fast on this path will cause you to fall.

ZH: 便道因为阴雨天的原因变得泥泞。
EN: The path became muddy due to the rainy weather.

ZH: 我们在便道上散步，享受着宁静的时光。
EN: We walk on the path, enjoying the peaceful time.
